                                <p style="text-transform: none; text-align: left; color:white;">You will receive an appraisal on any:</p>
                                <p style="text-transform: none; text-align: left; color:white; padding-top: 15px;">
                                    - diamond, gemstone, pearl, gold, or platinum item priced over $100 <br>
                                    - on any custom made diamond jewelry <br>
                                    - any loose diamond or engagement ring</p>
                            </span>
                        </span></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="tooltip"><span style="cursor: default;" class="u-color-dark-gray u-text-upper u-f16 u-text-none-underline">Free fedexÂ® shipping
                            <span class="tooltiptext" style="text-transform: none;">
                                <p style="text-transform: none; text-align: left; color:white;">Free Shipping</p>
                                <p style="text-transform: none; text-align: left; color:white;">We are happy to offer Free Fully Insured FedEx Shipping on All Orders worldwide. Once your order is processed it goes through a quality check inspection - after our final approval it is neatly packaged in our distinctive jewelry box and secured with all your documentation and shipped to you insured with FedEx Air. As soon as it ships we will send you an email with the tracking information.</p>
                            </span>
                        </span></td>
                        <td><span class="u-color-dark-gray u-text-upper u-f16 u-text-none-underline">Fully insured to your door</span></td>
